    • Method Detail

      • from

        @Nonnull
public static ClassInfo from(@Nonnull
                                       PersistentEObject object)
        Creates a new ClassInfo from the given object. The EClass will be found by calling the EObject.eClass() method.

        This method behaves like: of(eClass.getName(), eClass.getEPackage().getNsURI()).

        Parameters:
        object - the object from which the EClass has to be retrieve with the EObject.eClass() method
        Returns:
        a new ClassInfo
        See Also:
        of(String, String)
